Hey everyone. Today is my birthday so here’s a rare photo of me. I want to thank all those who support me and show me love. It’s definitely gotten me through some tough times and I’m forever grateful to have friends all around the world. I was somewhat uninspired for a few years if I’m honest and that has recently changed as I’ve been shooting more and took up a few other new hobbies. I look forward to new places, new faces and the new challenges that lie ahead. Focus on the positives, practice gratitude daily and give others the benefit of the doubt as we’re all just here for such a short time ❤️ 📸: @the_lost_coast
